N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 332.1 - Establishment

State Regulations

In accordance with the provisions of the Education Law, there shall be a council at each State- operated institution and, in the case
of the State University College of Environmental Science and Forestry, a board
of trustees. Notes
